{"tid":2442311,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"胡志偉擬於獄中修讀學位 　寄語市民：保重自己　避免送頭　要守住還可以守住的地方","createTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T09:31:21.000Z","uid":271829,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7b716e3943cf84405044e736704fb5ca5fc50351","tid":2442311,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gvQSIPvDEQ81OYpmL6x_I7vObLU=/2337x1314/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I7EQ5O2SYRF77IASO5GSX5CLQM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgvQSIPvDEQ81OYpmL6x_I7vObLU%3D%2F2337x1314%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI7EQ5O2SYRF77IASO5GSX5CLQM.JPG&h=28e7a260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡志偉至今已被還柙超過三個月，他透過邵家臻叮囑港人要保重。資料圖片<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n民主黨前主席胡志偉由今年初被還柙至今，已經有2個月時間。前議員邵家臻今日（11日）探訪過胡後表示，胡已適應監房生活，並打算修讀正規學位課程，同時，胡亦寄語大家「保重自己，避免送頭」。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻和另一前議員莫乃光今日探訪過胡志偉。邵透過社交網站表示，胡志偉甫見他們兩人便「笑容滿面，充滿力量」，胡亦已知悉其當友黃碧雲成功保釋，他希望更多人可獲保釋。邵續指，胡志偉已算適應了監房的生活，並計劃修讀正規課程，希望在囚期間能完成學位。由於現時胡被單獨囚禁，所以有很多時間讀書，邵形容，胡志偉「甚至乎要慳啲慳啲咁讀，怕一下子讀晒6本書」；而胡現感興趣的議題正是公共財政。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉亦透過邵家臻表示，他對自己已有最壞的打算，同時亦叮囑大家，「要保重自己，避免送頭」，「此刻或者可做的不多，但要守住還可以守住的地方，伺機而動。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/FUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FFUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=bf826278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FFUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4%2F&h=c5790443\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/FUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4/</a>"},{"pid":"c36577943d603fa409d100eb2aa6a3add1bcb0b0","tid":2442311,"uid":171302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b716e3943cf84405044e736704fb5ca5fc50351","tid":2442311,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/gvQSIPvDEQ81OYpmL6x_I7vObLU=/2337x1314/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/I7EQ5O2SYRF77IASO5GSX5CLQM.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FgvQSIPvDEQ81OYpmL6x_I7vObLU%3D%2F2337x1314%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FI7EQ5O2SYRF77IASO5GSX5CLQM.JPG&h=28e7a260&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n胡志偉至今已被還柙超過三個月，他透過邵家臻叮囑港人要保重。資料圖片<br />\n(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n民主黨前主席胡志偉由今年初被還柙至今，已經有2個月時間。前議員邵家臻今日（11日）探訪過胡後表示，胡已適應監房生活，並打算修讀正規學位課程，同時，胡亦寄語大家「保重自己，避免送頭」。<br />\n<br />\n邵家臻和另一前議員莫乃光今日探訪過胡志偉。邵透過社交網站表示，胡志偉甫見他們兩人便「笑容滿面，充滿力量」，胡亦已知悉其當友黃碧雲成功保釋，他希望更多人可獲保釋。邵續指，胡志偉已算適應了監房的生活，並計劃修讀正規課程，希望在囚期間能完成學位。由於現時胡被單獨囚禁，所以有很多時間讀書，邵形容，胡志偉「甚至乎要慳啲慳啲咁讀，怕一下子讀晒6本書」；而胡現感興趣的議題正是公共財政。<br />\n<br />\n胡志偉亦透過邵家臻表示，他對自己已有最壞的打算，同時亦叮囑大家，「要保重自己，避免送頭」，「此刻或者可做的不多，但要守住還可以守住的地方，伺機而動。」<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/FUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FFUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4%2F&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHT2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=bf826278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210311%2FFUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4%2F&h=c5790443\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210311/FUPBK4TDKVD37LBHAHW4Y5SGA4/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:26:16.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d0fbbef13065a9da8ef508c5f15bd1a8d61e5a","tid":2442311,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T09:26:17.000Z","msg":"香港仲有乜嘢可以守住 <i